definitions.definition: British , New Zealand , and India standard spelling of program .
examples: Our programme for today’s exercise class includes swimming and jogging.
The programme about Greek architecture starts at 9:00 on Channel 4.
ITEC is the Indian Technical and Economic Cooperation Programme .
